properties.areaDesc: Waters from Pigeon Point to Point Pinos 10-60 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 4 at 2:02PM PST until February 5 at 9:00PM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...For the first Small Craft Advisory, seas 7 to 11 feet
at 12 seconds. For the second Small Craft Advisory, northwest
winds 15 to 20 kt with gusts up to 30 kt expected.

* WHERE...Waters from Pigeon Point to Point Pinos 10-60 NM.

* WHEN...For the Small Craft Advisory, until 3 AM PST Wednesday.
For the Small Craft Advisory, from 3 PM to 9 PM PST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 AM PST WEDNESDAY... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 PM TO 9 PM PST WEDNESDAY
